a unite.vm plugin for Zend Framework(PHP).

inspired by basyura's unite-rails and oppara's unite-cake
https://github.com/basyura/unite-rails
https://github.com/oppara/vim-unite-cake

unite /app
  :Unite zf/app
unite /app/controllers
  :Unite zf/controllers
unite /app/models
  :Unite zf/models
unite /app/views
  :Unite zf/views
unite /app/views/helpers
  :Unite zf/helpers
unite /app/configs
  :Unite zf/configs
unite /app/layouts
  :Unite zf/layouts
unite /app/modules
  :Unite zf/modules
unite /app/tests
  :Unite zf/tests
unite /app/services
  :Unite zf/services
